text: Lincoln Center is a tall high-rise office building located 1660 Lincoln Street in Denver, Colorado. It was completed in 1972 and has 30 floors. According to Skyscraperpage.com, it is the 26th tallest building in Denver.Skyscraperpage.com Denver ==See also== *List of tallest buildings in Denver ==References== Category:Skyscraper office buildings in Denver Category:Office buildings completed in 1972
title: Lincoln Center (Denver)
